title: Awake and Aware - Volume 2C (NTSC Version)
description:
A conglomeration of several political activist documentaries together on one "movie" DVD. This is an attempt at packing the biggest "punch" in one DVD title. I call the DVD's, "Awake & Aware" after a similarly titled conference in LA September 2009. Enjoy and please spread around :)

P.S. a few mentionables in the DVD:

Conspiracy Theory, Season 1, Episode 1 (HAARP)
Conspiracy Theory, Season 1, Episode 2 (9/11)
Conspiracy Theory, Season 1, Episode 3 (Global Warming)
Conspiracy Theory, Season 1, Episode 4 (Big Brother)
Conspiracy Theory, Season 1, Episode 5 (Bilderbergs, Global Death Plot)
Conspiracy Theory, Season 1, Episode 6 (Manchurian Candidate)
Conspiracy Theory, Season 1, Episode 7 (2012)
Shadow Government
Dr Bill Deagle - Granada Forum, 2006
